<p><strong>“坚信爱会赢”</strong></p>
<p><strong>“向奋斗在一线的战‘疫’英雄们致敬”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201107/a35e2406463644719b58fa68a1b035e4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201107/fb25b2cc58fd430983320f4b22ab5a2b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
